(45, 'Fresh Studio Innovations Asia Ltd. No. 1A, Alley 275, Au Co Street, Tay Ho District, Hanoi Fresh Studio is an international professional services firm engaged in consulting, research and development (R&D) within the fresh produce industry. We offer the expertise and creativity needed to add value to the products and processes of companies operating in the entire value chain for fresh produce. Our offices in Vietnam are in Hanoi, Dalat, HCMC, and Can Tho. Our multi-disciplinary team consists of highly talented professionals with diverse cultural backgrounds. We believe that diversity is an essential ingredient for exceptional and creative solutions. Together with our clients and partners we work on a wide range of strategies in the areas of pre-harvest, post-harvest and marketing. Company Size: 25-99 Contact Person: Ms. Vu Thi Thanh Tam 1. Job identification     Position: HR & Admin Assistant     Vị trí: Nhân viên Hành chính – Nhân sự     Department: HR & Admin Department     Phòng ban: Phòng nhân sự     Location: Can Tho     Nơi làm việc: Trạm trung chuyển Thủy hải sản Siêu thị Metro Cần Thơ, P.Hưng Lợi, Q.Ninh Kiều, TP.Cần Thơ2. Key Organizational Relationships     Reports to: HR Supervisor in Hanoi     Báo cáo cho: Giám sát nhân sự – Văn phòng Hà Nội3. Primary objective     Mục tiêu     Togetherwith the HR team to sustain the on-going organization and business growth. The successor for this position will be based in Can Tho Collection Center and be responsiblefor implementing all aspects of human resources processes, programs and systems in Can Tho Collection Center (CTCC).     Ứng viên thành công cho vị trí này có nhiệm vụ cùng phòng nhân sự xây dựng và ổn định hoạt động của Công ty đang trong giai đoạn phát triển kinh doanh, chịu trách nhiệm thực thi tất cả những vấn đề liên quan đến quy trình, chương trình và hệ thống nhân sự tại trung tâm thu gom thủy hải sản – Siêu thị Metro Cần Thơ.4. Duties and responsibilities     Nhiệm vụ và trách nhiệm   Human resources management   Quản lý nhân sự     To deliver high quality HR services and provide professional advice and support in human resources issues.     Cung cấp các dịch vụ tư vấn nhân sự chuyên nghiệp, hỗ trợ các vấn đề liên quan đến quản lý con người trong Công ty.     Implement processes, procedures and policies.     Triển khai quy trình, quy định và thủ tục Hành chính nhân sự     Proactively support in recruitment and selection process for CTCC and arrange new hire orientation for new staff.     Chủ động hỗ trợ việc tuyển dụng và sắp lịch đào tạo định hướng cho nhân viên mới.     Handle employees'' disciplinary matters and material responsibilities.     Thực hiện các thủ tục liên quan đến quản lý kỷ luật lao động, trách nhiệm vật chất.     Monitor all issues of labor contract terms, terminations and resignations of the contracted employees in CTCC.     Quản lý và thực hiện các quy trình liên quan đến hợp đồng lao động, giải quyết các thủ tục thôi việc cho lao động.     Handle payroll calculation.     Tính lương cho lao động tại trung tâm thu gom thủy sản tại Cần Thơ     Other tasks are assigned by direct supervisor from time to time.     Thực hiện các nhiệm vụ khác theo hướng dẫn của cấp Quản lý trực tiếp.   Administrative management   Công việc Hành chính     Monitor staff’s leaves and attendance.     Thực hiện chấm công và quản lý phép cho nhân viên     Control stationary and labor protection tools, issue to staff as and when needed.     Quản lý văn phòng phẩm, dụng cụ lao động, phát cho nhân viên khi cần.     Check all administrative expenses for CTCC and make requests for payment and cash advancement on AMS system. Monitor monthly cash management and quarterly forecast.     Quản lý và thực hiện các thủ tục thanh toán trên hệ thống AMS cho các chi phí hành chính của Trạm trung chuyển thủy hải sản Cần Thơ. Quản lý tiền mặt và dự trù chi phí tiền mặt hàng quý.     Oversee office administration matters and suggest to solve/ improve     Quản lý và đề xuất các giải pháp cho các vấn đề hành chính tại trạm trung chuyển.     To perform other tasks assigned by the management.     Các nhiệm vụ khác theo chỉ đạo của các cấp quản lý khi phát sinh.   5. Desired qualifications     Kỹ năng mong muốn   Minimum requirements   Bằng cấp tối thiểu     University graduate major in Human Resources Management or Business Administration.    Cử nhân tốt nghiệp ngành Quản trị nhân lực hoặc quản trị kinh doanh hoặc các ngành có liên quan.   Experience:   Kinh nghiệm     Minimum 02 years of relevant experience     Tối thiểu 2 năm kinh nghiệm ở cùng vị trí hoặc các công việc có liên quan.   Special Skills required:   Kỹ năng khác     Good knowledge of the Labor Law and HR related regulation     Có kiến thức cơ bản về luật lao động và các vấn đề liên quan đến quản lý con người     Strong interpersonal and communication skills     Có khả năng giao tiếp tốt     High level of ethics and confidentiality     Hiểu rõ các vấn đề về đạo đức và bảo mật thông tin.     Professional in English communication both verbal and written.     Sử dụng Tiếng Anh thành thạo (nói và viết)     Action oriented, pro-active analytical, organized     Khả năng thực thi tốt, phân tích tốt, chủ động và có kế hoạch.     Responsible, meticulous and positive working attitude     Có trách nhiệm, tỉ mỉ, tinh thần làm việc tích cực.     Proficiency in MS Office     Sử dụng thành thạo ứng dụng văn phòng We offer competitive salaries and are very dedicated to invest in the development of our talents. If you think you can add value to our team, you can send your application letter and resume through e-mail before July the 24 st 2015 to: tam.vu@freshstudio.vn', '', '2015-08-03 17:00:00', '02 NHÂN VIÊN KINH DOANH', 'CT', '<tr><td bgcolor="#ffffff">\r\n		<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="3" id="table2" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">\n<tr>\n<td class="text" align="left">\r\n				<img border="0" src="logo/logo-freshstudio.jpg" width="93" height="70">\n</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				<b><font size="4" face="Times New Roman">Fresh Studio \r\n				Innovations Asia Ltd.</font></b>\n</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				<p style="margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px">\r\n				No. 1A, Alley 275, Au Co Street, Tay Ho District, Hanoi</p>\n</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				<p align="justify" style="line-height: 165%; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px">\r\n				Fresh Studio is an international professional services firm \r\n				engaged in consulting, research and development (R&amp;D) within the \r\n				fresh produce industry. We offer the expertise and creativity \r\n				needed to add value to the products and processes of companies \r\n				operating in the entire value chain for fresh produce. Our \r\n				offices in Vietnam are in Hanoi, Dalat, HCMC, and Can Tho. Our \r\n				multi-disciplinary team consists of highly talented \r\n				professionals with diverse cultural backgrounds. We believe that \r\n				diversity is an essential ingredient for exceptional and \r\n				creative solutions. Together with our clients and partners we \r\n				work on a wide range of strategies in the areas of pre-harvest, \r\n				post-harvest and marketing.</p>\n</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				Company Size: 25-99</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				<p align="justify" style="line-height: 160%; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px">\r\n				Contact Person: Ms. Vu Thi Thanh Tam</p>\n</td>\r\n			</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="text">\r\n				<p align="justify" style="line-height: 170%; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px">\r\n				<b>1. Job identification</b><br>\r\n 